skill.description:
Gain 20% Move Speed. When the Dance Level reaches 1, gain 15% Attack Speed.Yae Sakura could remember traveling peddlers setting up stalls outside the village every month or so. These peddlers will often sell strange crafts not found inside the village.These memories were the reasons why strange merchants would appear in the Stigmata Space.
Seele received this present from "mom" in the orphanage.
